OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FAn asylum seeker who smiled and stuck
OL,7,Fhis tongue out to his friend while he
OL,8,Fwas allegedly raping a woman on
OL,9,FBrighton beach has denied "celebrating
OL,10,Fher humiliation".
OL,12,FIbrahim Alshafe, 25, is on trial
OL,13,Falongside co-defendants Karin Al-
OL,14,FDanasurt, 20, and Abdulla Ahmadi, 26,
OL,15,Ffor allegedly targeting the woman in
OL,16,Fthe early hours of 4 October last year.
OL,18,FAlshafe and Ahmadi are accused of
OL,19,Frepeatedly raping the woman on the
OL,20,Fbeach, while Al-Danasurt filmed the
OL,21,Fincident.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@PO]
