FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FGiving evidence at Hove Crown Court,
OL,7,FAlshafe said he believed the woman
OL,8,Fwanted to have sex with him, adding:
OL,9,F"I swear I didn't rape her."
OL,11,FThe Egyptian national previously told
OL,12,Fthe trial the woman had approached
OL,13,Fhimself and Ahmadi, kissing them and
OL,14,Ftouching them so their understanding
OL,15,Fwas she wanted to have sex.
OL,17,FIn a video shown to jurors at Hove
OL,18,FCrown Court, Alshafe is seen smiling
OL,19,Fwith his tongue out and making a hand
OL,20,Fgesture towards his friend Al-Danasurt
OL,21,Fwho was filming.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FBut he said he didn't know he was
OL,7,Fbeing filmed, and instead was reacting
OL,8,Fto his friend making a hand gesture at
OL,9,Fhim first.
OL,11,FPut to him in cross-examination by
OL,12,Fprosecutor Hanna Llewellyn-Waters KC
OL,13,Fthat he was celebrating her
OL,14,Fhumiliation, he replied: "This is not
OL,15,Fcelebration, this a reaction to a
OL,16,Fgesture that was made to me."
OL,18,FSpeaking through an Arabic
OL,19,Finterpreter, he also told jurors: "I
OL,20,Fwas happy, she was happy."
OL,26,@vD@ZOUxD@]O]{D@cOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
