PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FAlshafe was also asked about a final
OL,7,Fthird recording that has been shown in
OL,8,Fcourt of him slapping the woman in the
OL,9,Fface.
OL,11,FHe said: "I wasn't hitting her to
OL,12,Fpunish her or torture her, I was
OL,13,Fplaying with her."
OL,15,FJurors have been told the woman had
OL,16,Fbeen separated from her friends while
OL,17,Fon a girls' night out, and prosecutors
OL,18,Fsaid the three defendants approached
OL,19,Fher when she was "staggering in the
OL,20,Fstreet" alone.
OL,26,@sD@JOUuD@RO]{D@ROU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
