PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FShe left the Horizon nightclub on the
OL,7,Feastern side of Brighton beach before
OL,8,Fheading to Burger King on Kings Road
OL,9,Faround 5:30am.
OL,11,FCCTV which has previously been shown
OL,12,Fin court shows the woman interacting
OL,13,Fwith the defendants outside Burger
OL,14,FKing.
OL,16,FThe group then cross Kings Road
OL,17,Ftogether on to the promenade and then
OL,18,Fon to the beach where the alleged
OL,19,Fincident took place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
