OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FThe court has heard that footage shows
OL,7,Fthe woman falling down twice. Asked if
OL,8,Fshe was unconscious at any time,
OL,9,FAlshafe answered no, and when asked if
OL,10,Fshe was asleep at any time, he
OL,11,Freplied: "No, she was enjoying what we
OL,12,Fwere doing."
OL,14,FHe said in the walk from the beach
OL,15,Fbefore and after the incident they
OL,16,Fwere kissing each other.
OL,26,@sD@JOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
