PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FAt the time of the alleged offences,
OL,7,Fall three defendants knew each other
OL,8,Fand were residents at a Home Office-
OL,9,Fapproved hotel accommodation for
OL,10,Fasylum seekers near Horsham in West
OL,11,FSussex.
OL,13,FGiving evidence in court, Alshafe
OL,14,Fadmitted he lied in his initial police
OL,15,Finterviews about not being in Brighton
OL,16,Fand said he was at his accommodation
OL,17,Fat the time of the incident.
OL,19,FOn Wednesday, he said: "I was scared,
OL,20,FI was terrified of what's going on."
OL,26,@{D@XOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
