FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775754356
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FAlshafe, of Lower Beeding, and Iranian
OL,7,Fnational Ahmadi, of Crewe in Cheshire,
OL,8,Fhave each denied two counts of raping
OL,9,Fthe woman.
OL,11,FEgyptian national Al-Danasurt, also of
OL,12,FLower Beeding, is jointly charged on
OL,13,Fall four rape counts as a secondary
OL,14,Fparty "encouraging the rape by his
OL,15,Factions at the scene, including
OL,16,Ffilming it", and has pleaded not
OL,17,Fguilty to all four charges.
OL,19,FHe denies a fifth count of "sharing
OL,20,Fintimate films" without the
OL,21,Fcomplainant's consent.
OL,26,@vD@GOUxD@KO]{D@\OU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
