OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of raping woman
OL,4,Cdenies 'celebrating her humiliation'
OL,6,FThe charge relates to an allegation
OL,7,Fthat Al-Danasurt sent recordings of
OL,8,Fthe alleged rapes to Ahmadi's phone
OL,9,Fvia Snapchat shortly after the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FThe trial continues.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
